fourth straight gold at that distance.\", \"from\": 3049, \"to\": 3114, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"China's\\u00a0Zhang Yufei, the reigning Olympic champion and of nearly two dozen swimmers from her country who tested positive for a banned substance ahead of the Tokyo Games but were\\u00a0allowed to compete,\\u00a0pushed the pace in the 200 fly over the first half of the race.\", \"from\": 3116, \"to\": 3377, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3116, \"end\": 3121, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9712566089942781, \"rank\": 0.02616581513768287, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3124, \"end\": 3135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhang_Yufei_(swimmer)\", \"score\": 0.9727864122994488, \"rank\": 0.027972027972036382, \"text\": \"Zhang Yufei\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhang_Yufei_(swimmer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhang_Yufei_(swimmer)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No way she was holding off McIntosh, though.\", \"from\": 3379, \"to\": 3423, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3406, \"end\": 3414, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.90296651638704e-16, \"text\": \"McIntosh\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 17-year-old powered to the lead on the third 50 and left no doubt on the closing lap.\", \"from\": 3425, \"to\": 3514, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She touched in an Olympic-record of 2:03.03.\", \"from\": 3515, \"to\": 3559, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Smith passed Zhang as well, but had no chance of chasing down the youngster who has established herself as one of the biggest stars at La Defense Arena.\", \"from\": 3561, \"to\": 3713, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"McIntosh opened the games with\\u00a0a silver medal\\u00a0in the 400 freestyle, finishing ahead of Katie Ledecky, and blew away the field in the\\u00a0400 individual medley.\", \"from\": 3715, \"to\": 3870, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3715, \"end\": 3723, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.90296651638704e-16, \"text\": \"McIntosh\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\"}, {\"begin\": 3802, \"end\": 3815, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katie Ledecky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This was another rout.\", \"from\": 3872, \"to\": 3894, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Smith touched in 2:03.84 for the fourth silver medal of her career, which has yet to produce a gold.\", \"from\": 3895, \"to\": 3995, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Zhang held on for the bronze in 2:05.09.\", \"from\": 3996, \"to\": 4036, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hungary's Hubert K\\u00f3s claimed gold in the 200 backstroke, another triumph for a swimmer coached by Bob Bowman.\", \"from\": 4038, \"to\": 4147, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4038, \"end\": 4045, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"score\": 0.8046543176427993, \"rank\": 0.24276969386000155, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\"}, {\"begin\": 4136, \"end\": 4139, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Bryan\", \"score\": 0.9999999803408175, \"rank\": 1.963991569446532e-08, \"text\": \"Bob\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Bryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Bryan\"}, {\"begin\": 4140, \"end\": 4146, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bowman\", \"score\": 0.9999999815149752, \"rank\": 1.8485235449191444e-08, \"text\": \"Bowman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bowman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bowman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"K\\u00f3s rallied on the final lap to pass Greece's Apostolos Christou.\", \"from\": 4149, \"to\": 4214, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4186, \"end\": 4192, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9821146886841532, \"rank\": 0.018211021092646874, \"text\": \"Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The winner finished in 1:54.26, while Christou held on for the silver in 1:54.82.\", \"from\": 4215, \"to\": 4296, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The bronze went to Roman Mityukov of Switzerland in 1:54.85.\", \"from\": 4297, \"to\": 4357, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4316, \"end\": 4330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roman_Mityukov\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Roman Mityukov\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roman_Mityukov\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roman_Mityukov\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bowman coached K\\u00f3s at Arizona State University, where he competed alongside the biggest swimming star of these games, France's L\\u00e9on Marchand.\", \"from\": 4359, \"to\": 4500, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4359, \"end\": 4365, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bowman\", \"score\": 0.9999999815149752, \"rank\": 1.8485235449191444e-08, \"text\": \"Bowman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bowman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bowman\"}, {\"begin\": 4381, \"end\": 4405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arizona_State_Sun_Devils\", \"score\": 0.7809396263236426, \"rank\": 0.2805065450565529, \"text\": \"Arizona State University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arizona_State_Sun_Devils\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arizona_State_Sun_Devils\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bowman now heads the program at the University of Texas, and K\\u00f3s has transferred to join him.\", \"from\": 4502, \"to\": 4595, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4502, \"end\": 4508, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bowman\", \"score\": 0.9999999815149752, \"rank\": 1.8485235449191444e-08, \"text\": \"Bowman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bowman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bowman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"K\\u00f3s praised Bowman, best known as Michael Phelps' coach, for pushing him to new heights.\", \"from\": 4597, \"to\": 4685, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4609, \"end\": 4615, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bowman\", \"score\": 0.9999999815149752, \"rank\": 1.8485235449191444e-08, \"text\": \"Bowman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bowman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bowman\"}, {\"begin\": 4631, \"end\": 4645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.1715486278050374e-95, \"text\": \"Michael Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's been an incredible journey with him, and I am just to happy be part of a team like that,\\\" K\\u00f3s said.\", \"from\": 4687, \"to\": 4792, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The magic touch is the work.\", \"from\": 4793, \"to\": 4822, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He does not let us be second best.\", \"from\": 4823, \"to\": 4857, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He does not let us stoop down to a level he does not want from us.\", \"from\": 4858, \"to\": 4924, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That brings out the best in us.\\\"\", \"from\": 4925, \"to\": 4957, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Marchand set himself up for another gold-medal run, posting the fastest time (1:56.31) in the semifinals of the men's 200 individual medley.\", \"from\": 4959, \"to\": 5099, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Already the winner of three gold medals, the French star is a big favorite to make it four in a row in the final Friday of his last individual event.\", \"from\": 5101, \"to\": 5250, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5146, \"end\": 5152, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.7964517101102728, \"rank\": 0.2311512801729974, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"American Carson Foster posted the second-fastest time (1:56.37).\", \"from\": 5252, \"to\": 5316, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5252, \"end\": 5260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999755133786821, \"rank\": 2.1185155946756883e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 5261, \"end\": 5274, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carson_Foster\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carson Foster\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carson_Foster\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carson_Foster\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After a close call in the morning preliminaries, American Caeleb Dressel will get a chance to defend his Olympic title in the 50 freestyle Friday night.\", \"from\": 5318, \"to\": 5470, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5367, \"end\": 5375, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999755133786821, \"rank\": 2.1185155946756883e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 5376, \"end\": 5390, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caeleb_Dressel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caeleb Dressel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caeleb_Dressel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caeleb_Dressel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dressel posted the fifth-fastest time in the evening semifinals (21.58) Thursday on the heels of tying for 13th in the heats.\", \"from\": 5472, \"to\": 5597, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Benjamin Proud of Britain and Cameron McEvoy of Australia shared the top spot in swimming's most chaotic race - an all-out dash from one end of the pool to the other - at 21.38.\", \"from\": 5598, \"to\": 5775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5598, \"end\": 5612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Proud\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Benjamin Proud\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid